This paper deals with the capacity region of multiple-input multiple-output massive multiple access channels (MIMO mMAC), which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network communications (cs.NI). The paper also utilizes Gallager's error exponent analysis, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the individual user rate and allocation of sum rate, which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer networks (cs.COM).
